{"tid":583684,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"BBC記者到北京街訪習近平登基 中國民眾：「非常民主，中國特色的民主」","createTime":"2018-03-07T08:09:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-08T05:36:25.000Z","uid":75969,"like":46,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"64a1b985e6e134ff27fe7a8573a542be91a18e02","tid":583684,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T08:09:13.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕習近平離稱帝越來越近，中國人大預計11日就會投票表決，討論是否廢除憲法中的國家主席任期限制。英國廣播公司（BBC）記者麥克唐納（Stephen McDonell）特地來到北京街頭，訪問中國民眾對於習近平當上終身領導人的意見，竟然有多名人民代表跟他說這是「民主」，讓麥克唐納當場滿臉問號。<br />\n<br />\n據《BBC》報導，一名身穿少數民族服裝的少女被訪問時，<span style=\"color: red;\">面帶微笑地說「這是新時代的需求。」</span>一位大媽則強調，這是為了國家的長治久安。麥克唐納隨後採訪一個大叔，<span style=\"color: red;\">他說習近平無任期限制「挺好的、民主」</span>，因為每個人的意見都可以表達。<br />\n<br />\n麥克唐納滿臉不解，連忙詢問大叔<span style=\"color: red;\">「你不怕給一個人那麼多權力嗎？」大叔則說「這是大家要選的嘛，大家選出來是什麼就是什麼的。」麥克唐納追問「那你要選什麼？」大叔回應「我現在還不能告訴你！」便離開現場。</span><br />\n<br />\n麥克唐納接著採訪到一名穿著少數民族服裝的婦人，她直說習近平沒了任期限制非常好，<span style=\"color: red;\">「體現了國家的民主」</span>，讓《BBC》記者無言以對。<br />\n<br />\n麥克唐納最後找上一個西裝阿伯，阿伯說習近平此舉對中國的發展非常好，因為始終是一個政權一直走。被問到是否會擔心極權時，阿伯連說不會，因為這樣<span style=\"color: red;\">「非常民主，中國特色的民主權力，是大家選出來的。」</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9PGSlKBfngI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9PGSlKBfngI&d=IYlurP2LEVsDKdiYVEe4owhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=cd56a1ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9PGSlKBfngI</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2356855\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2356855&d=IYlurP2LEVsDKdiYVEe4owhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=0c8d6f1d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2356855&h=8b5ec8d5\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2356855</a><br />\n<br />\n習帝深得民心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"491ef7f6e9f3ab1d33dcb1f132667a6a1e6e0c1a","tid":583684,"uid":43231,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T08:11:39.000Z","msg":"弄愚民於股掌之中<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e90340ea64f3b489ea302dd0fc3a5867913fca46","tid":583684,"uid":33028,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T08:16:14.000Z","msg":"民主中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d363e09594b8a4adc328da3ef7c37771892a310","tid":583684,"uid":57376,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T08:19:25.000Z","msg":"做媒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03a0a35f5c95ebbf13bcff1b088fa3e6625b2f55","tid":583684,"uid":70846,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T08:20:58.000Z","msg":"梗係民主啦呢啲西方人都唔q識嘅<br />\n偉大嘅支共國係間選國家主席㗎嘛<br />\n那村呢就可以選村代表，村代表選舉鎮代表，鎮代表就可以選市代表，市代表就可以選人大代表，人大就選國家主席，係國家最高權力機關，立法制定政策，幾民主<br />\n<br />\n只不過，所有可以投票嘅內容都係共產黨決定姐，有份投票架喇幾民主"},{"pid":"bcf1ef3c73c15b07ec037c0f358e5ff70598d622","tid":583684,"uid":4525,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T08:21:01.000Z","msg":"民+主=民主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0537495b843e9f4bedae3c1bbb84319785757a76","tid":583684,"uid":56157,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"491ef7f6e9f3ab1d33dcb1f132667a6a1e6e0c1a","tid":583684,"uid":43231,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T08:11:39.000Z","msg":"弄愚民於股掌之中<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src